# List of Sites of Special Scientific Interest in Warwickshire

This is a list of the Sites of Special Scientific Interest (SSSIs) in Warwickshire. English Nature, the designating body for SSSIs in England, uses the 1974â€“1996 county system. The majority of these sites are locally managed by the Warwickshire Wildlife Trust.
For other counties, see List of SSSIs by Area of Search.
